OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain, heavy at times through
OL,6,Fthe morning, gradually eases away
OL,7,Fsouth and east through the afternoon.
OL,8,FSome brighter or sunny spells
OL,9,Ffollowing, but feeling rather chilly,
OL,10,Fespecially in the breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry and settled, with
OL,13,Fclearing skies overnight allowing
OL,14,Ftemperatures to fall, feeling cold
OL,15,Fwith some ground frost patches
OL,16,Fpossible. Winds light but breezy along
OL,17,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
